  {
   "start": 27.26,
   "end": 31.96,
   "text": "And then I was, um, got back."
  },
  {
   "start": 32.2,
   "end": 35.06,
   "text": "So then I had to go to sleep, and I slept until, like, 2 or 3 or whatever."
