  {
   "start": 61.91,
   "end": 62.67,
   "text": "No, no, no, Polybius."
  },
  {
   "start": 63.61,
   "end": 74.09,
   "text": "And then I was really happy with myself for how quickly and accurately I was making the links."
  },
  {
   "start": 74.09,
   "end": 79.73,
   "text": "You know, like, I, because this, the, the books on my website work really well like that."
