  {
   "start": 104.81,
   "end": 106.15,
   "text": "And then you just know you can zero in."
  },
  {
   "start": 106.19,
   "end": 106.81,
   "text": "That's really cool."
  },
  {
   "start": 107.93,
   "end": 114.75,
